      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario geometry, fluid properties, and operating conditions are representative of the CPB COU; similarity metrics documented.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump — the same platform as the COU device. Blood analog fluid (glycerin-water) used in experiments; viscosity and density matched within 3% of clinical blood properties. Operating envelope spans the clinical CPB range. Relevance level 2 achieved."
    },
