      "rationale": "Formal use error assessment not required at MRL 2. Lead analyst holds PhD in computational fluid dynamics with 8 years of cardiovascular device simulation experience. Simulation setup peer-reviewed internally. Factor not-assessed per MRL 2 scope."
    },
    {
