      "rationale": "RANS k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating blood-contacting devices. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) adopted per FDA guidance. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2; selection rationale documented."
    },
